name: Libérez Vous
description:
Will release on August 1st at 3p.m. 

Designed by Reggie Aluyi

100% Cotton

-Fits true to size.
-Gold, side zippers
-Machine wash cold, Tumble dry low.

Libérez Vous represents freedom, it is french for "Free Yourself" when you feel trapped in your own thoughts,  no one around to help you, they say we are still free, but we truly remain prisoners. The Chinese symbols on the tee represent freedom also. I just always felt as if I was trapped in my own thoughts. The back of the t-shirt means "this is only the beginning". If you don't take care of what needs to be taken care of time will not wait for you...
Ce n'est que le début means "This is only the beginning", This is my start...
